\
**Key Responsibilities:**\
\
1. **Front-End Development:** Design, develop, and implement user interfaces across multiple platforms using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript frameworks.\
   \
2. **Responsive Design:** Ensure seamless responsiveness and compatibility across various devices and browsers.\
\
3. **Collaboration:** Work closely with designers, UX/UI specialists, and back-end developers to bridge the gap between graphical design and technical implementation.\
\
4. **Prototyping and Wireframing:** Transform design wireframes into functional prototypes, iterating on user feedback and implementing changes as needed.\
\
5. **Optimization:** Continuously optimize UI components for maximum speed and scalability, focusing on performance improvements.\
